<item>
            <title>[LU-6741] OSP should use inline data for small requests</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6741</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;we shouldn&apos;t use bulks to transfer updates unless it&apos;s needed. otherwise all &quot;interactive&quot; requests (like lookups, getattrs, etc) need 2 RTTs instead of one.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
